parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Plastic Fuel Tank Expansion and Loosening
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The expansion and loosening of the plastic fuel tank can cause the tank to detach from the motorcycle, leading to a hazardous situation, loss of steering control, and potential accidents.
symptoms: The fuel tank spreads or expands
causing it to become loose on the frame
the tank wobbles and can be lifted from the frame
the handlebars hit the tank on turning
small cracks in the plastic form around the fuel tank filler and checker.
